import React, { useState, useEffect } from "react"; import { Link } from "react-router-dom"; import { FontAwesomeIcon } from '@fortawesome/react-fontawesome'; import { faBoxOpen, faCartArrowDown, faChartPie, faChevronDown, faClipboard, faCommentDots, faFileAlt, faPlus, faRocket, faStore } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons'; import Profile3 from "../../assets/img/team/profile-picture-3.jpg"; import setAuthToken from "../validation/authAuthToken"; const axios = require('axios').default; export default () => { let initialState = { full_name: "", email: "", country_code: "", country: "", phone_number: "", } const [link, setLink] = useState("") const [form, setForm] = useState(initialState) const [profile, setProfile] = useState([]); const [message, setMessage] = useState(""); const [errorClass, setErrorClass] = useState(""); let token = localStorage.getItem("token"); useEffect(() => { let token = localStorage.getItem("token"); setAuthToken(token); fetchProfile(token) }, []) let formHandler = async (e) => { let { name, value, checked } = e.target if (checked == true && name == "privacy_status") { setForm({ ...form, [name]: 1 }) } else if (checked == false && name == "privacy_status") { setForm({ ...form, [name]: 0 }) } else { setForm({ ...form, [name]: value }) } } let fetchProfile = async (token) => { try { const response = await axios.get(`${process.env.REACT_APP_SERVER_URL}/api/profile`, { headers: { 'authorization': `Bearer ${token}`, 'Content-Type': 'application/json' } }) let res = response.data if (res.status === true && res.code === 200) { setProfile(res.data) setForm({...form, full_name: res.data.full_name}) setForm({...form, email: res.data.email}) setForm({...form, full_name: res.data.full_name}) setForm({...form, full_name: res.data.full_name}) console.log(res.data) } } catch (err) { console.error(err); } } let submitUpdate = async (e) => { e.preventDefault() setMessage("") setErrorClass('') let data = { "full_name": "king doe", "country_code": "234", "phone_number": "929393939", "country": "nigeria" } try { const response = await axios.post(`${process.env.REACT_APP_SERVER_URL}/api/update-personal-info`, data, { headers: { 'authorization': `Bearer ${token}`, 'Content-Type': 'application/json' } }) let res = response.data if (res.status === false && res.code === 422) { setErrorClass('text-white bg-danger rounded-1 my-2 px-2') res.errors.amount[0] && setMessage(res.errors.amount[0]) res.errors.plan_id[0] && setMessage(res.errors.plan_id[0]) } else if (res.status === true && res.code === 200) { setMessage(res.message) setErrorClass('text-white bg-success rounded-1 my-2 px-2') } else if (res.status === false && res.code === 423) { setMessage(res.message) setErrorClass('text-white bg-danger rounded-1 my-2 px-2') } } catch (err) { console.error(err);
